03:22.577 --> 03:24.204
<i>Their country home in Great Neck</i>

03:24.371 --> 03:26.669
<i>was the pantheon
of summer gatherings.</i>

03:26.832 --> 03:28.926
<i>On the eve of his 51st year,</i>

03:29.084 --> 03:31.678
<i>Jean-Louis took Conrad's mother
to the south of France</i>

03:31.837 --> 03:34.590
<i>on what was to be
a weekend excursion.</i>

03:34.756 --> 03:38.386
<i>It had since turned into
a lavish escapade around the world</i>

03:38.552 --> 03:41.021
<i>lasting nearly three decades.</i>

03:41.179 --> 03:45.104
<i>Over the subsequent years, Conrad
was raised by the Valmont's staff.</i>

03:45.267 --> 03:47.065
<i>His chauffeur Bernard</i>

03:47.227 --> 03:49.229
<i>had taken Conrad
