03:55.736 --> 03:57.784
<i>It was a family tradition.</i>

03:58.822 --> 04:02.543
<i>At present, he was working
on his magnum opus -</i>

04:02.701 --> 04:04.248
<i>a great New York novel</i>

04:04.411 --> 04:07.460
<i>in the tradition
of Fitzgerald and Edith Wharton.</i>

04:07.622 --> 04:08.999
<i>It was widely speculated</i>

04:09.166 --> 04:11.464
<i>as to where he was
in the process of writing it.</i>

04:11.626 --> 04:13.674
<i>When asked, he would simply reply...</i>

04:13.837 --> 04:15.384
I'm in the gathering stages.

04:15.547 --> 04:18.642
<i>Conrad had been
in the "gathering stages"</i>

04:18.800 --> 04:21.144
<i>for several years now.</i>

04:21.303 --> 04:24.307
<i>Last week Thursday,
