06:52.162 --> 06:54.585
<i>Herein lies the eternal question</i>

06:54.748 --> 06:56.876
<i>is it a grocery list</i>

06:57.042 --> 06:59.795
<i>or her phone number?</i>

07:02.088 --> 07:05.934
